Package: dds
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Description: Distributed Data Service
 The Data Distribution Service for Real-Time Systems (DDS) is an Object
 Management Group (OMG) machine to machine middleware "m2m" standard that
 aims to enable scalable, real-time, dependable, high performance and
 interoperable data exchanges between publishers and subscribers.

